      • progressLocation

        public short progressLocation
        Specifies the progress location in a Progress Indicator Information Element from the PRI network. Possible values are PL_NONE, PL_USER, PL_PUB_LOCAL, PL_PUB_REMOTE, PL_PRIV_REMOTE

      • progressDescription

        public short progressDescription
        Specifies the progress description in a Progress Indicator Information Element from the PRI network. Possible values are PD_NONE, PD_CALL_OFF_ISDN, PD_DEST_NOT_ISDN, PD_ORIG_NOT_ISDN, PD_CALL_ON_ISDN, PD_INBAND
